name: Nee_Tonna
content:
Nee Tonna was a Cathar male who, by 3630 BBY, was wanted by the Eternal Empire for theft, sabotage and operating a cantina without a license. He was last seen in the lower levels of the Empire's capital Zakuul and his wanted poster was displayed in the Overwatch.
Nee Tonna appears during Chapter 10: Anarchy in Paradise of Star Wars: The Old Republic: Knights of the Fallen Empire on a wanted holo-poster.
